      },
      {
        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "込高・新田高（こみだか・しんでんだか）。免（めんりつ）三ッ八分七八厘貳毛七弗 ＝ 約〇・三八七八。朱書（赤インクの書き入れ）。"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "A red-ink (朱書) marginal note continuing the 但内 column above it. It states that the 但内 figure (246,015.67 koku) is 込高・新田高 — incorporated-high plus new-field-high, i.e. the reclamation uplift booked above the 540,000-koku formal rating — and records the menritsu (assessed land-tax rate) on that uplift as 三ッ八分七八厘貳毛七弗, about 0.3878."
      },
      {
        "purpose": "identifying",
        "value": "但内 込高新田高（免・朱書）"
